<section id="faq" class="bg-slate-50 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-3xl space-y-6">
      <details class="rounded-xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6" open>
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">How do point deductions work?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Setting up campsite monitors is free. Points are deducted only after CampSoon helps you successfully book a campsite. Each successful booking uses exactly 1,000 points.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="rounded-xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Does CampSoon automate checkouts or payment transactions?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          No. CampSoon behaves strictly as a speed UI assistant. It captures cancellations and forwards your active browser tab to the official park reservation checkout, where you input payment data securely through the reservation provider's own processing infrastructure.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
